				<div class="et_pb_promo_description"><h2 class="et_pb_module_header">NO Current Closure</h2><div><p>During the week of Monday, February 8, sub-zero wind chills are expected. Please make sure your children take home their Chromebooks each day to make sure they can attend school virtually if weather prevents us from meeting in person</p>
<p>A final decision will be made on 3pm on Sunday, February 6, as to whether we shall hold in-person classes on Monday, February 8. Please check your email and texts for updates.&nbsp;</p>
<p>While the covid-19 virus is still affecting our communities, The Einstein Academy IS open for in-person learning for prek-2. While grades 3-12 are being taught remotely;&nbsp; we hope to have them back in the building soon!&nbsp;</p>
<p><span style="font-size: 14px;">As always, if you have any questions or concerns, need help or advice, or just want someone to talk to, please feel free to reach out to me ANY time at&nbsp;</span><a href="https://web.archive.org/web/20220626075038/mailto:cilani@einsteinacademy.us" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" style="font-size: 14px;"><span class="il">cilani</span>@einsteinacademy.us</a><span style="font-size: 14px;">.</span></p>
<p><span>xo</span><br><span>~Mrs. Ilani</span></p></div></div>
				
